document.full_text: germany's andrea petkovic sobbed during a changeover but set up a second round clash against jelena jankovic after battling past austrian qualifier tamira paszek 3-6 6-2  in stuttgart on tuesday.
document.title: sobbing petkovic sets up stuttgart clash with jankovic
